==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scyllarian
<hw>Scyl*la"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>One of a family (<fam>Scyllaridae</fam>) of macruran Crustacea,
remarkable for the depressed form of the body, and the broad, flat
antennae. Also used adjectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scyllite</ent>⟦br⟧
